Source: cortex-llm
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Cortex Linux Team <team@cortexlinux.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://cortexlinux.com
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/cortexlinux/cortex-distro
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/cortexlinux/cortex-distro.git
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: cortex-llm
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 cortex-core,
 python3 (>= 3.11),
 python3-pip,
 python3-venv,
 python3-numpy,
 python3-scipy,
 python3-pandas,
 libopenblas0,
 libblas3,
 liblapack3
Recommends:
 python3-torch,
 python3-transformers,
 build-essential,
 python3-dev
Suggests:
 cortex-gpu-nvidia | cortex-gpu-amd,
 cortex-model-tiny,
 ollama
Provides: cortex-llm-backend
Description: Cortex Linux local LLM runtime support
 This meta-package provides local LLM inference capabilities
 for Cortex Linux, enabling offline AI operations.
 .
 Features:
  - PyTorch inference runtime
  - Transformers library support
  - CPU-optimized inference (default)
  - GPU acceleration when available
 .
 For GPU-accelerated inference, also install:
  - cortex-gpu-nvidia (NVIDIA GPUs)
  - cortex-gpu-amd-rocm (AMD GPUs)
 .
 Pre-packaged models available:
  - cortex-model-tiny (CPU-friendly, ~500MB)
  - cortex-model-base (balanced, ~2GB)
  - cortex-model-large (high-quality, ~8GB)

Package: cortex-model-tiny
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 cortex-llm
Description: Cortex Linux tiny LLM model package
 A small, CPU-friendly language model for basic Cortex operations.
 .
 Model characteristics:
  - Size: ~500MB
  - Memory: ~2GB RAM
  - Inference: CPU-optimized
  - Quality: Good for simple tasks
 .
 This model is suitable for:
  - Package management assistance
  - Basic system queries
  - Simple natural language commands
  - Offline operation on low-resource systems

Package: cortex-model-base
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 cortex-llm
Recommends:
 cortex-gpu-nvidia | cortex-gpu-amd
Description: Cortex Linux base LLM model package
 A balanced language model for Cortex operations.
 .
 Model characteristics:
  - Size: ~2GB
  - Memory: ~8GB RAM (16GB with GPU)
  - Inference: CPU or GPU
  - Quality: Good for most tasks
 .
 This model is suitable for:
  - Complex system administration tasks
  - Code generation and analysis
  - Detailed explanations
  - Multi-step operations
